org.activebpel.rt.message

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.message
org.activebpel.rt.axis Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).  
org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.receivers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity This package contains classes which define the various BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity.support This package contains classes which support various BPEL activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity This package contains implementation classes for activity validation models. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.activity.wsio This package contains validation model implementation classes for WSIO related validation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity This package contains classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.assign.to This package contains implementation classes used when executing the 'to' portion of an assign activity's copy operation. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.consume Provides interfaces and classes for consuming WSDL message data by BPEL activities and other supporting objects (e.g., invoke activity, receive activity, and onEvent element of a pick activity).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.produce Provides interfaces and classes for producing WSDL message data from BPEL activities (e.g., invoke and reply).  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.queue Contains classes that model inbound and outbound messages from the engine as well as alarms.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage Classes related to saving and restoring the state of processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.invoke   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process This package contains classes related to process management.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.receive   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.journal This package contains classes for representing journal entries for alarms, messages, or faults for possible recovery in the event of engine failure. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.recovered This package contains classes for representing alarm or queue manager items recovered during the course of process recovery. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.test This package contains classes for testing the functionality of the recovery engine. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.reply   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.xpath
